<chapter id="remoting_resource">
	<title>Resources</title>
	<para>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem>
				<para>Download</para>
				<para>
					Download anyframe-sample-remoting.zip file containing example code in the following and extract those files.
					<itemizedlist>
						<listitem>
							<para>Maven-based run</para>
							<para>
								After moving to extracted folder in the command window,
								execute command named 'mvn clean test' and check the execution result.					
							</para>
						</listitem>
						<listitem>
							<para>Eclipse-based run</para>
							<para>
								After importing extracted project on Eclipse,
								select any Test class under src/test/java,
								and click mouse right button and click on Run As > JUnit Test on the context menu. Check the execution result.							
							</para>
						</listitem>									
					</itemizedlist>
				</para>
				<table>
					<title>Download List</title>
					<tgroup cols="2">
